{"tid":1491987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新海誠有野想同香港人講","createTime":"2019-08-20T15:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T16:48:13.000Z","uid":241240,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4553abcd96d1e3f93aa011070c0fa836e63a570","tid":1491987,"uid":241240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"上完新海誠堂天空之子，係心態上學識左啲野:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為手足嘅犧牲而感到傷心，根本就係一種矛盾<br />\n因為手足係為緊 &quot;大家所相信嘅晴天&quot; 去犧牲<br />\n傷心呢種情感只會係 &quot;否定緊佢地嘅努力&quot;<br />\n<br />\n大家要記得新海誠老師有提到，世界原本就係 &quot;雨天&quot; <br />\n&quot;晴天&quot; 只係普世價值下嘅一種好現象 (大家所相信嘅美好)<br />\n如果你有份去相信同追求 &quot;晴天&quot;，但同時又對晴女被活祭而感到傷心<br />\n咁你唯有好似男主角咁飛上天救翻晴女落地 (<span style=\"color: gold;\">good end</span>)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但現實係︰</span></span></strong><br />\n你飛唔撚起阿，接受因為你嘅信仰而衍生出黎嘅犧牲啦 (就好似大叔果個角色咁 <span style=\"color: blue;\">bad end</span>)<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\npossible argument: <br />\n我傷心係因為我相信晴天唔一定要晴女嘅犧牲換番黎<br />\n<br />\ncounter argument:<br />\n屌，你同新海誠講"},{"pid":"d202e32bd2eab742c4f45a4a2ff78582b344c8e8","tid":1491987,"uid":2562,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXcMrux.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXcMrux.jpg&h=54112853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN4V4gd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN4V4gd.jpg&h=bf41982c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/20/233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F20%2F233941_35db8952adc66a9b8fad2b475503a348.jpeg&h=ba2d15e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img s